section ‚ÄπUltraproduct construction‚Ä∫

theory UltraConstruction_ZF imports Ultrafilter_ZF EquivClass1
begin

text‚ÄπThis theory deals with the ultra product construction, internal entities
and some basic properties of them.‚Ä∫

locale ultra = 
  fixes ùîâ and I and X
  assumes ultraFilter:"ùîâ{is an ultrafilter on}I" and nonEmpty:"‚àÄi‚ààI. X(i)‚â†0"

begin

text‚ÄπWe define an equivalence relation‚Ä∫

definition hyper_rel where
"hyper_rel ‚â° {‚ü®f,g‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. f`n = g`n}‚ààùîâ}"

text‚ÄπThe relation is reflexive‚Ä∫

lemma hyper_refl:
  shows "refl(Pi(I,X),hyper_rel)" unfolding refl_def
proof-
  {
    fix x assume x:"x:Pi(I,X)"
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n = x`n} = I" by auto moreover
    have "I‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n = x`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with x have "‚ü®x,x‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  }
  then show "‚àÄx‚ààPi(I, X). ‚ü®x, x‚ü© ‚àà hyper_rel" by auto
qed

text‚ÄπThe relation is symmetric‚Ä∫

lemma hyper_sym:
  shows "sym(hyper_rel)" unfolding sym_def
proof(safe)
  fix x y assume "‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà hyper_rel"
  then have as:"x:Pi(I,X)" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚ààùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  {
    fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}"
    then have "n‚ààI" "x`n=y`n" by auto
    then have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. y`n = x`n}" by auto
  } moreover
  {
    fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. y`n = x`n}"
    then have "n‚ààI" "y`n=x`n" by auto
    then have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}" by auto
  } ultimately
  have "{n‚ààI. y`n = x`n} = {n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}" by blast
  with as(3) have "{n‚ààI. y`n = x`n} :ùîâ" by auto
  with as(1,2) show "‚ü®y,x‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
qed

text‚ÄπThe relation is transitive‚Ä∫

lemma hyper_trans:
  shows "trans(hyper_rel)" unfolding trans_def
proof(safe)
  fix x y z assume as:"‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà hyper_rel" "‚ü®y, z‚ü© ‚àà hyper_rel"
  then have A:"x:Pi(I,X)" "z:Pi(I,X)" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  {
    fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n = z`n}"
    then have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}" by auto
  }
  then have sub:"{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n = z`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}" by auto
  from as(1,2) have "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n = z`n}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
    unfolding hyper_rel_def IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
  then have "‚àÄA‚ààPow(I). {n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n = z`n} ‚äÜ A ‚ü∂ A‚ààùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  ultimately have "({n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n = z`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}) ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}‚ààùîâ"
    by auto
  with sub have "{n‚ààI. x`n = z`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
  with A show "‚ü®x, z‚ü© ‚àà hyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
qed

text‚ÄπThe relation is an equivalence‚Ä∫

lemma hyper_equiv:
  shows "equiv(Pi(I,X), hyper_rel)" unfolding equiv_def
  using hyper_refl hyper_sym hyper_trans apply auto
  unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto

definition hyper_set where
"hyper_set ‚â° Pi(I,X)// hyper_rel"

lemma incl_inj:
  fixes Y
  assumes "‚àÄi‚ààI. X(i) = Y"
  defines "incl ‚â° {‚ü®x,hyper_rel``{ConstantFunction(I,x)}‚ü©. x‚ààY}"
  shows "incl‚ààinj(Y,hyper_set)" unfolding inj_def
proof(safe)
  {
    fix x assume x:"x:Y"
    then have "ConstantFunction(I,x):I‚ÜíY" using func1_3_L1 by auto
    then have "ConstantFunction(I,x)‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def Sigma_def using assms(1) by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{ConstantFunction(I,x)}‚ààhyper_set" unfolding hyper_set_def
      quotient_def by auto
  }
  then have "‚àÄx‚ààY. hyper_rel``{ConstantFunction(I,x)}‚ààhyper_set" by auto
  then show f:"incl:Y‚Üíhyper_set" using ZF_fun_from_total unfolding incl_def by auto
  {
    fix w x assume as:"w:Y" "x:Y" "incl ` w = incl ` x"
    then have e:"hyper_rel``{ConstantFunction(I,w)} = hyper_rel``{ConstantFunction(I,x)}"
      using apply_equality[OF _ f] unfolding incl_def by auto
    from as(1,2) have c:"ConstantFunction(I,w):I‚ÜíY" "ConstantFunction(I,x):I‚ÜíY"
      using func1_3_L1 by auto
    then have cc:"ConstantFunction(I,w)‚ààPi(I,X)" "ConstantFunction(I,x):Pi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def Sigma_def using assms(1) by auto
    with e have "‚ü®ConstantFunction(I,w),ConstantFunction(I,x)‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using same_image_equiv[of "Pi(I,X)" "hyper_rel"]
      hyper_equiv by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ConstantFunction(I,w)`n = ConstantFunction(I,x)`n}:ùîâ"
      unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. w = x}:ùîâ" using func1_3_L2 by auto
    then show "w=x" using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
  }
qed

lemma hyper_set_structure:
  assumes "‚àÄi‚ààI. P(i):X(i)√óX(i)‚ÜíX(i)"
  defines "Q ‚â° {‚ü®‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©,{‚ü®i,P(i)`‚ü®q1`i,q2`i‚ü©‚ü©. i‚ààI}‚ü©. ‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X)}"
  shows "Congruent2(hyper_rel, Q)" "Q:Pi(I,X)√óPi(I,X) ‚Üí Pi(I,X)"
    "‚àÄi‚ààI. ‚àÄx‚ààPi(I,X). ‚àÄy‚ààPi(I,X). Q`‚ü®x,y‚ü©`i = P(i)`‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©"
  unfolding Congruent2_def hyper_rel_def apply safe apply auto
proof-
  {
    fix x y assume xy:"x‚ààPi(I,X)" "y‚ààPi(I,X)"
    {
      fix i assume i:"i:I"
      with xy have "x`i:X(i)" "y`i:X(i)" using apply_type by auto
      with assms(1) have "P(i)`‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©‚ààX(i)" using apply_type i by auto
    }
    then have "{‚ü®i,P(i)`‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,X)"
      unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  }
  then have "‚àÄx‚ààPi(I, X) √ó Pi(I, X).
       (Œª‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©. {‚ü®i, P(i) ` ‚ü®q1 ` i, q2 ` i‚ü©‚ü© . i ‚àà I})(x) ‚àà Pi(I, X)" by auto moreover
  have "Q={‚ü®x, (Œª‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©. {‚ü®i, P(i) ` ‚ü®q1 ` i, q2 ` i‚ü©‚ü© . i ‚àà I})(x)‚ü© . x ‚àà Pi(I, X) √ó Pi(I, X)}"
    unfolding Q_def by force
  ultimately show qF:"Q:Pi(I,X)√óPi(I,X)‚ÜíPi(I,X)" unfolding Q_def 
    using ZF_fun_from_total[of "Pi(I,X)√óPi(I,X)" "Œª‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©. {‚ü®i,P(i)`‚ü®q1`i,q2`i‚ü©‚ü©. i‚ààI}" "Pi(I,X)"]
    by auto
  then have "‚àÄx‚ààPi(I,X). ‚àÄy‚ààPi(I,X). Q`‚ü®x,y‚ü© = {‚ü®i,P(i)`‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
    using apply_equality unfolding Q_def by auto moreover
  from qF have "‚àÄx‚ààPi(I,X). ‚àÄy‚ààPi(I,X). Q`‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)"
    using apply_type by auto ultimately
  have R:"‚àÄi‚ààI. ‚àÄx‚ààPi(I,X). ‚àÄy‚ààPi(I,X). Q`‚ü®x,y‚ü©`i = P(i)`‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©"
    using apply_equality[where A=I and B=X] by auto
  then show "‚ãÄi x y. i ‚àà I ‚üπ x ‚àà Pi(I, X) ‚üπ y ‚àà Pi(I, X) ‚üπ Q ` ‚ü®x, y‚ü© ` i = P(i) ` ‚ü®x ` i, y ` i‚ü©" by auto
  fix x y z t
  assume as:"{n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n} ‚àà ùîâ"
       "x ‚àà Pi(I,X)" "y ‚àà Pi(I,X)" "{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n} ‚àà ùîâ"
       "z ‚àà Pi(I,X)" "t ‚àà Pi(I,X)"
  from qF as(2,5) show "Q`‚ü®x,z‚ü©:Pi(I,X)" using apply_type by auto
  from qF as(3,6) show "Q`‚ü®y,t‚ü©:Pi(I,X)" using apply_type by auto
  {
    fix n assume "n‚àà{n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n}"
    then have "n‚ààI" "x ` n = y ` n" "z ` n = t ` n" by auto
    then have "P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©" by auto
    with `n‚ààI` have "n‚àà{n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}" by auto
  }
  then have "{n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n} ‚äÜ {n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}"
    by blast
  moreover from as(1,4) have "{n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
  then have "‚àÄA‚ààPow(I). {n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n} ‚äÜ A ‚ü∂ A:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
  then have "{n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}‚ààPow(I) ‚ü∂ (({n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n} ‚äÜ {n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}) ‚ü∂ {n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}:ùîâ)"
    by auto
  then have "({n ‚àà I . x ` n = y ` n}‚à©{n ‚àà I . z ` n = t ` n} ‚äÜ {n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}) ‚ü∂ {n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}:ùîâ" by auto
  ultimately have "{n ‚àà I . P(n)`‚ü®x`n,z`n‚ü© = P(n)`‚ü®y`n,t`n‚ü©}:ùîâ" by auto
  then show "{n ‚àà I . Q`‚ü®x,z‚ü©`n = Q`‚ü®y,t‚ü©`n}:ùîâ"
    using R as(2,3,5,6) by auto
qed

subsection‚ÄπInternal sets‚Ä∫

definition internal_set where
"S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i))) ‚üπ internal_set(S) ‚â° {hyper_rel``{x}. x‚àà{x‚ààPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ}}"

lemma internal_subset:
  assumes "S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"
  shows "internal_set(S) ‚äÜ hyper_set"
proof-
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_set(S)"
    then have "t‚àà{hyper_rel``{x}. x‚àà{x‚ààPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ}}"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms].
    then obtain q where q:"t=hyper_rel``{q}" "q:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ"
      by auto
    from q(1,2) have "t‚ààhyper_set" unfolding hyper_set_def quotient_def by auto
  }
  then show "internal_set(S) ‚äÜ hyper_set" by auto
qed

lemma internal_sub:
  assumes "S1:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"  "S2:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚ààùîâ"
  shows "internal_set(S1) ‚äÜ internal_set(S2)"
proof
  fix x assume "x‚ààinternal_set(S1)"
  then obtain xx where x:"xx‚ààPi(I,X)" "x=hyper_rel``{xx}" "{n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
  from x(3) assms(3) have "{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
    unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS2`n}" by auto
  ultimately have "{n‚ààI. xx`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def
    by auto
  with x(1,2) show "x‚ààinternal_set(S2)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(2)] by auto
qed

lemma internal_sub_rev:
  assumes "S1:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"  "S2:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" 
  and "internal_set(S1) ‚äÜ internal_set(S2)"
  and "Pi({i‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`i‚äÜS2`i)},Œªj. S1`j-S2`j) ‚â† 0" (* We can choose elements in the difference*)
  and "Pi(I,X)‚â†0"
  shows "{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚ààùîâ"
proof-
  from assms(5) obtain y where y:"y‚ààPi(I,X)" by auto
  from assms(4) obtain x where x:"x‚ààPi({i‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`i‚äÜS2`i)},Œªj. S1`j-S2`j)" by auto
  let ?u="{‚ü®i,if S1`i‚äÜS2`i then y`i else x`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  {
    fix n assume "n‚ààI"
    {
      assume "S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n"
      then have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n) = y`n" by auto
      then have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n)‚ààX(n)" using apply_type `n‚ààI` y by auto
    } moreover
    {
      assume as:"¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)"
      then have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n) = x`n" by auto
      moreover have "n‚àà{i‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`i‚äÜS2`i)}" using `n‚ààI` as by auto
      then have "x`n‚ààS1`n - S2`n" using apply_type[OF x, of n] by auto
      ultimately have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n)‚ààS1`n-S2`n" using apply_type x `n‚ààI` x as by auto
      then have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n)‚ààS1`n" by auto
      then have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n)‚ààX(n)" using apply_type[OF assms(1) `n‚ààI`] by blast 
    }
    ultimately have "(if S1`n‚äÜS2`n then y`n else x`n)‚ààX(n)" by auto
  }
  then have u:"?u‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  then have R:"‚ãÄn. n‚ààI ‚üπ ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n) ‚üπ ?u`n=x`n" using apply_equality by auto
  {
    assume as:"{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚àâùîâ"
    with as have "I-{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter set_ultrafilter[of _ I ùîâ] by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} = I-{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}" by auto
    ultimately have F1:"{n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    {
      fix j assume "j‚àà{n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)}"
      then have j:"j‚ààI" "¬¨(S1`j ‚äÜ S2`j)" by auto
      with x have "x`j ‚àà S1`j - S2`j" using apply_type[OF x] by auto
      then have "x`j‚ààS1`j" "x`j‚àâS2`j" by auto
      with R j have "?u`j‚ààS1`j" "?u`j‚àâS2`j" by auto
    }
    then have F2:"{n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS1`n}" "{n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n}" by auto
    from ultraFilter have "‚ãÄC. C‚äÜI ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} ‚äÜ C ‚üπ C‚ààùîâ"
      using F1 unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS1`n}‚äÜI ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS1`n} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ"
     "{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n}‚äÜI ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ¬¨(S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with F2 have U:"{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ" "{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    from U(1) u have u1:"hyper_rel``{?u}‚ààinternal_set(S1)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)]
      by auto
    have "I-{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n} = {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚àâS2`n}" by auto
    with U(2) have "I-{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    then have "I-(I-{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n})‚àâùîâ" using ultraFilter only_set_or_opposite[of "I-{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}" I]
      unfolding IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    moreover have "I-(I-{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}) = {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}" by auto
    ultimately have M:"{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚àâùîâ" by auto
    {
      fix q assume "q‚ààPi(I,X)" "hyper_rel``{q} = hyper_rel``{?u}"
      then have "‚ü®q,?u‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using same_image_equiv[OF hyper_equiv] u by auto
      then have A:"{n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚ààùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
      {
        assume "{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ"
        with A have AA:"{n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def
          using is_filter_def_split(4) by auto
        moreover have B:"{n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}" by auto
        from AA ultraFilter have "‚ãÄC. C‚äÜ I ‚üπ {n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n} ‚äÜ C ‚üπ C‚ààùîâ"
          unfolding IsUltrafilter_def using is_filter_def_split(5) by auto
        then have "{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚äÜI ‚üπ{n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" 
          by auto
        then have "{n‚ààI. q`n = ?u`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
        with B have "{n‚ààI. ?u`n‚ààS2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
        with M have False by auto
      }
      then have "{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààS2`n}‚àâùîâ" by auto
    }
    then have "hyper_rel``{?u}‚àâinternal_set(S2)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(2)] by auto
    with u1 assms(3) have False by auto
  }
  then show ?thesis by auto
qed

corollary internal_eq:
  assumes "S1:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"  "S2:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "{n‚ààI. S1`n = S2`n}‚ààùîâ"
  shows "internal_set(S1) = internal_set(S2)"
proof
  have "{n‚ààI. S1`n = S2`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}" "{n‚ààI. S1`n = S2`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. S2`n ‚äÜ S1`n}" by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}:Pow(I)" "{n‚ààI. S2`n ‚äÜ S1`n}:Pow(I)" by auto
  moreover note assms(3) ultimately have A:"{n‚ààI. S1`n ‚äÜ S2`n}:ùîâ" "{n‚ààI. S2`n ‚äÜ S1`n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  from A(1) show "internal_set(S1) ‚äÜ internal_set(S2)" using internal_sub[OF assms(1,2)] by auto
  from A(2) show "internal_set(S2) ‚äÜ internal_set(S1)" using internal_sub[OF assms(2,1)] by auto
qed

lemma internal_total_set:
  shows "internal_set({‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}) = hyper_set"
proof
  have f:"{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_set({‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})"
    then have "t‚àà{hyper_rel``{x}. x‚àà{x‚ààPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ}}"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF f].
    then obtain q where q:"t=hyper_rel``{q}" "q:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. q`n‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ"
      by auto
    from q(1,2) have "t‚ààhyper_set" unfolding hyper_set_def quotient_def by auto
  }
  then show "internal_set({‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}) ‚äÜ hyper_set" by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààhyper_set"
    then obtain q where q:"t=hyper_rel``{q}" "q:Pi(I,X)" unfolding hyper_set_def
        quotient_def by auto
    from f have R:"‚àÄn‚ààI. {‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n = X(n)" using apply_equality by auto
    from q(2) have "‚àÄn‚ààI. q`n‚ààX(n)" using apply_type by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààX(n)} = I" by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. q`n‚ààX(n)}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def
      by auto
    with R have "{n‚ààI. q`n‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with q(2) have "q‚àà{x‚ààPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ}" by auto
    with q(1) have "t‚àà{hyper_rel``{x}. x‚àà{x‚ààPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ}}" by auto
    then have "t:internal_set({‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f].
  }
  then show "hyper_set ‚äÜ internal_set({‚ü®i,X(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
qed

lemma internal_inter:
  assumes "isInternal(A)" "isInternal(B)"
  shows "isInternal(A‚à©B)"
proof-
  from assms obtain SA SB where s:"SA:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "SB:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" 
    "A=internal_set(SA)" "B=internal_set(SB)"
    unfolding isInternal_def by auto
  let ?S="{‚ü®n,(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)‚ü©. n‚ààI}"
  from s(1,2) have "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SA`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SB`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" using apply_type[of _ I "Œªi. Pow(X(i))"]
    by auto
  then have "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" by auto
  then have f:"?S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix t assume t:"t‚ààinternal_set(?S)"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà?S`n}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
    from x(3) have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)}‚ààùîâ"
      using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
    then have R:"‚àÄA‚ààPow(I). {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)} ‚äÜ A ‚ü∂ A‚ààùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}" by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with x(1,2) have A:"t‚ààinternal_set(SA)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)] by auto
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
    with R have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©(SB`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n}" by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with x(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(SB)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(2)] by auto
    with A have "t‚ààA‚à©B" using s(3,4) by auto
  }
  then have "internal_set(?S) ‚äÜ A‚à©B" by auto moreover
  {
    fix t assume t:"t‚ààA‚à©B"
    with s(3,4) obtain ta tb where t:"t=hyper_rel``{ta}" "ta‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. ta`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ"
      "t=hyper_rel``{tb}" "tb‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. tb`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààùîâ" unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)]
      internal_set_def[OF s(2)] by blast
    from t(1,4) have "hyper_rel``{ta}=hyper_rel``{tb}" by auto
    then have "‚ü®ta,tb‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using same_image_equiv[OF hyper_equiv] t(5) by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ta`n=tb`n}:ùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    with t(3) have "{n‚ààI. ta`n=tb`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ta`n‚ààSA`n}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    with t(6) have "{n‚ààI. ta`n=tb`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ta`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. tb`n‚ààSB`n}:ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "‚àÄA‚ààPow(I). {n‚ààI. ta`n=tb`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ta`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. tb`n‚ààSB`n}‚äÜA ‚ü∂ A:ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. ta`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©SB`n} :Pow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. ta`n=tb`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ta`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. tb`n‚ààSB`n}‚äÜ{n‚ààI. ta`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©SB`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. ta`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©SB`n}:ùîâ"
      by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ta`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à©SB`n}:ùîâ" by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ta`n‚àà{‚ü®n, SA ` n ‚à© SB ` n‚ü© . n ‚àà I}`n}:ùîâ"
      using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
    with t(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
  }
  then have "A‚à©B ‚äÜ internal_set(?S)" by auto
  ultimately have "A‚à©B = internal_set(?S)" by auto
  then show ?thesis unfolding isInternal_def using f by auto
qed

lemma complement_internal:
  assumes "isInternal(A)"
  shows "isInternal(hyper_set-A)"
proof-
  from assms obtain SA where s:"SA:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"
    "A=internal_set(SA)" unfolding isInternal_def by auto

      unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
    {
      assume "t‚ààinternal_set(SA)"
      then obtain y where y:"t=hyper_rel``{y}" "y‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ"
        unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)] by auto
      from x(1) y(1) have "‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using y(2) same_image_equiv
          hyper_equiv by auto
      then have "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚ààùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
      with y(3) have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}‚ààùîâ"
        using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
      then have "‚ãÄA. A‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n} ‚äÜ A ‚üπ A:ùîâ"
        using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
      then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}:ùîâ" by auto
      moreover have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}" by auto
      ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}: ùîâ" by auto
      with x(3) have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-(SA`n)}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
        apply_equality[OF _ f]
        unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto moreover
      {
        fix n assume n:"n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-(SA`n)}"
        then have False by auto
      }
      then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-(SA`n)} = 0" by auto
      ultimately have "0‚ààùîâ" by auto
      then have False using ultraFilter
        unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    }
    then have "t‚àâinternal_set(SA)" by auto moreover
    have "t‚ààhyper_set" using internal_subset[OF f] t by auto
    ultimately have "t‚ààhyper_set-A" using s(2) by auto
  }
  then have "internal_set(?S) ‚äÜ hyper_set-A" by auto moreover

    then have "I-{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ" using set_ultrafilter[OF _ ultraFilter]
      by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-SA`n}‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ I-{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-SA`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààX(n)-SA`n}:ùîâ"

    with x(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
  }
  ultimately have "hyper_set-A = internal_set(?S)" by auto
