lemma finite_internal:
  assumes "A‚ààFinPow(hyper_set)"
  shows "isInternal(A)" unfolding isInternal_def
proof(rule FinPow_induct[OF _ _ assms])
  let ?S0="I√ó{0}"
  have s:"?S0:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_set(?S0)"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà?S0`n}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF s] by auto
    from x(3) have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà0}‚ààùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ s] by auto
    then have "0‚ààùîâ" by auto
    then have False using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  }
  then have "0 = internal_set(?S0)" by auto
  with s show "‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). 0 = internal_set(S)" by auto
  {
    fix B assume b:"B‚ààFinPow(hyper_set)" "‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). B = internal_set(S)"
    from b(2) obtain S where S:"S:(‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "B=internal_set(S)" by auto

    {
      fix t assume "t‚ààhyper_set"
      then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x:Pi(I,X)" unfolding hyper_set_def
        quotient_def by auto
      let ?S="{‚ü®i,S`i‚à™{x`i}‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
      have f:"?S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto
        using apply_type[OF x(2)] apply_type[OF S(1)] by auto
      {
        fix q assume q:"q‚ààB‚à™{t}"
        {
          assume "q‚ààB"
          with S(2) obtain y where y:"q=hyper_rel``{y}" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n}:ùîâ"
            unfolding internal_set_def[OF S(1)] by auto
          have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n‚à™{x`n}}" by auto
          moreover from y(3) have "‚ãÄQ. Q ‚äÜ I ‚üπ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n} ‚äÜ Q ‚üπ Q:ùîâ"
            using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
          from this[of "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n‚à™{x`n}}"] 
          have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n‚à™{x`n}} ‚üπ {n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n‚à™{x`n}}:ùîâ" by auto
          ultimately have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n‚à™{x`n}}:ùîâ" by auto
          then have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚àà?S`n}:ùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
          with y(1,2) have "q‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
        } moreover
        {
          assume "q‚àâB"
          with q have "q=t" by auto
          with x have xx:"q=hyper_rel``{x}" "x:Pi(I,X)" by auto
          have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{x`n}} = I" by auto
          then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{x`n}}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def
            IsUltrafilter_def by auto
          then have "‚ãÄQ. Q ‚äÜ I ‚üπ {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{x`n}} ‚äÜ Q ‚üπ Q:ùîâ"
            using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
          from this[of "{n:I. x`n:?S`n}"] have 
            "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{x`n}} ‚äÜ {n:I. x`n:?S`n} ‚üπ {n:I. x`n:?S`n}:ùîâ" by auto
          moreover
          have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{x`n}} ‚äÜ {n:I. x`n:?S`n}" using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
          ultimately have " {n:I. x`n:?S`n}:ùîâ" by auto
          with xx have "q‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
        } ultimately
        have "q:internal_set(?S)" by auto
      }
      then have "B‚à™{t} ‚äÜ internal_set(?S)" by auto moreover
      {
        fix q assume q:"q‚ààinternal_set(?S)" "q‚â†t"
        then obtain y where y:"q=hyper_rel``{y}" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n:I. y`n:?S`n}:ùîâ"
          unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
        {
          assume "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n}‚àâùîâ"
          then have "I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
            set_ultrafilter[of _ I, OF _ ultraFilter] by auto
          with y(3) have "(I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n})‚à©{n:I. y`n:?S`n}:ùîâ"
            using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
          then have "‚ãÄB. B:Pow(I) ‚üπ (I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n})‚à©{n:I. y`n:?S`n} ‚äÜ B ‚üπ B:ùîâ"
            using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
          from this[of "{n:I. y`n=x`n}"] have "(I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n})‚à©{n:I. y`n:?S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. y`n=x`n} ‚üπ {n:I. y`n=x`n}:ùîâ"
            by auto moreover
          {
            fix h assume "h:(I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n})‚à©{n:I. y`n:?S`n}"
            then have "h‚ààI" "y`h‚àâS`h" "y`h‚àà?S`h" by auto
            then have "h‚ààI" "y`h = x`h" using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
            then have "h:{n:I. y`n=x`n}" by auto
          }
          then have "(I-{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n})‚à©{n:I. y`n:?S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. y`n=x`n}" by auto
          ultimately have "{n:I. y`n=x`n}:ùîâ" by auto
          with x(2) y(2) have "‚ü®y,x‚ü©:hyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
          then have "q=t" using x(1) y(1) equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv] by auto
          with q(2) have False by auto
        }
        then have "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
        with y(1,2) have "q‚ààB" using S(2) unfolding internal_set_def[OF S(1)] by auto
      }
      then have "internal_set(?S) ‚äÜ B‚à™{t}" by auto
      ultimately have "B‚à™{t} = internal_set(?S)" by auto
      with f have "‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). B ‚à™ {t} = internal_set(S)" by auto
    }
    then have "‚àÄt‚ààhyper_set. ‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). B ‚à™ {t} = internal_set(S)" by auto
  }
  then show "‚àÄA‚ààFinPow(hyper_set).
       (‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). A = internal_set(S)) ‚ü∂
       (‚àÄt‚ààhyper_set. ‚àÉS‚àà‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)). A ‚à™ {t} = internal_set(S))" by auto
qed

lemma internal_union:
  assumes "isInternal(A)" "isInternal(B)"
  shows "isInternal(A‚à™B)"
proof-
  from assms obtain SA SB where s:"SA:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "SB:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" 
    "A=internal_set(SA)" "B=internal_set(SB)"
    unfolding isInternal_def by auto
  let ?S="{‚ü®n,(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)‚ü©. n‚ààI}"
  from s(1,2) have "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SA`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SB`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" using apply_type[of _ I "Œªi. Pow(X(i))"]
    by auto
  then have "‚àÄn‚ààI. (SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)‚ààPow(X(n))" by auto
  then have f:"?S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix t assume t:"t‚ààinternal_set(?S)"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà?S`n}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
    from x(3) have U:"{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚ààùîâ"
      using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
    {
      assume "t‚àâA"
      with x(1,2) s(3) have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)}‚àâùîâ" unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)]
        by auto
      then have "I-{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
        set_ultrafilter[of "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)}"] by auto moreover
      have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}‚ààPow(I)" by auto moreover
      {
        fix n assume "n‚ààI-{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)}"
        then have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}" by auto
      }
      then have "I-{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}" by auto
      ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def
        IsUltrafilter_def by auto
      with U have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}:ùîâ"
        using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
      have "{n:I. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto moreover
      {
        fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)}"
        then have "n‚ààI" "x`n‚ààSB`n" by auto
        then have "n:{n:I. x`n‚ààSB`n}" by auto
      }
      then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. x`n‚àâ(SA`n)} ‚äÜ {n:I. x`n‚ààSB`n}" by auto
      ultimately have "{n:I. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def
        IsUltrafilter_def by auto
      with x(1,2) have "t‚ààB" using s(4) unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(2)] by auto
    }
    then have "t‚ààA‚à™B" by auto
  }
  then have "internal_set(?S) ‚äÜ A‚à™B" by auto moreover
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààA"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n}‚ààùîâ"
      using s(3) unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)] by auto
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSA`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}" by auto moreover
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚ààPow(I)" by auto moreover note x(3)
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà?S`n}:ùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
    with x(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
  }
  then have "A ‚äÜ internal_set(?S)" by auto moreover
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààB"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n}‚ààùîâ"
      using s(4) unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(2)] by auto
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààSB`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}" by auto moreover
    have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}‚ààPow(I)" by auto moreover note x(3)
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà(SA`n)‚à™(SB`n)}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà?S`n}:ùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ f] by auto
    with x(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF f] by auto
  }
  then have "B ‚äÜ internal_set(?S)" by auto ultimately
  have "A ‚à™ B = internal_set(?S)" by auto
  then show ?thesis unfolding isInternal_def using f by auto
qed

definition elevatedProp ("^_^" 90) where
"^P^ ‚â° Œªt. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y}=t"

lemma internal_subset_internal:
  assumes "isInternal(A)"
  shows "isInternal({x‚ààA. (^P^)(x)})"
proof-
  from assms obtain S where s:"S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))"
    "A=internal_set(S)" unfolding isInternal_def by auto
  let ?S="{‚ü®i,{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  {
    fix i assume i:"i‚ààI"
    then have "{x‚ààS`i. P(x)} ‚äÜ S`i" by auto
    with s(1) have "{x‚ààS`i. P(x)} ‚äÜ X(i)" using apply_type[OF _ i, of S "Œªi. Pow(X(i))"] by auto  
  }
  then have ss:"?S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚àà{x‚ààA. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = x}"
    then obtain y where t:"t‚ààA" "y‚ààPi(I,X)" "{i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ" "hyper_rel``{y} = t" by auto
    from t(1,4) have "hyper_rel``{y}‚ààinternal_set(S)" using s(2) by auto
    then obtain z where z:"hyper_rel``{y} = hyper_rel``{z}" "z‚ààPi(I,X)" "{i‚ààI. z`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)] by auto
    from z(1) have "‚ü®y,z‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using same_image_equiv[OF hyper_equiv] z(2) by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. y`i = z`i}‚ààùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    with z(3) have "{i‚ààI. y`i = z`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. z`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    moreover have "{i‚ààI. y`i = z`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. z`i‚ààS`i} = {i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i}" by auto
    ultimately have "{i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" by auto moreover
    have "{i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}" by auto moreover
    have "‚ãÄC. C‚äÜI ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i} ‚äÜ C ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ ‚üπ C‚ààùîâ" 
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i} ‚äÜ I ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i} ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i = z`i ‚àß y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    ultimately have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with t(3) have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def 
      IsFilter_def by auto moreover
    have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. P(y`i)} = {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}" by auto
    ultimately have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà?S`i}‚ààùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ ss] by auto
    with t(2,4) have "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF ss] by auto
  }
  then have "{x‚ààA. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = x} ‚äÜ internal_set(?S)" by auto moreover
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_set(?S)"
    then obtain y where t:"t=hyper_rel``{y}" "y‚ààPi(I,X)" "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà?S`i}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF ss] by auto
    from t(3) have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}‚ààùîâ" using apply_equality ss by auto
    moreover have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}" "{i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}" by auto
    moreover have "‚ãÄC. C‚äÜI ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}} ‚äÜ C ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}‚ààùîâ ‚üπ C‚ààùîâ" 
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsUltrafilter_def IsFilter_def by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚äÜI ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i} ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}‚ààùîâ ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" 
      "{i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚äÜI ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. P(y`i)} ‚üπ {i‚ààI. y`i‚àà{x‚ààS`i. P(x)}}‚ààùîâ ‚üπ {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    ultimately have "{i‚ààI. y`i‚ààS`i}‚ààùîâ" "{i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    with t(1,2) have "t‚ààinternal_set(S)" "‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = t"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF s(1)] by auto
    with s(2) have "t‚àà{x‚ààA. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = x}" by auto
  }
  then have "internal_set(?S) ‚äÜ {x‚ààA. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = x}" by auto
  ultimately have "{x‚ààA. ‚àÉy‚ààPi(I,X). {i‚ààI. P(y`i)}‚ààùîâ ‚àß hyper_rel``{y} = x} = internal_set(?S)" by auto
  then show ?thesis unfolding isInternal_def using ss unfolding elevatedProp_def by auto
qed

          
definition internal_rel where
"S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i))) ‚üπ internal_rel(S) ‚â° {‚ü®hyper_rel``{x},hyper_rel``{y}‚ü©. ‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®p,q‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. ‚ü®p`n,q`n‚ü©‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ}}"

lemma internal_rel_subset:
  assumes "S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  shows "internal_rel(S) ‚äÜ hyper_set√óhyper_set"
proof-
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_rel(S)"
    then have "t‚àà{‚ü®hyper_rel``{x},hyper_rel``{y}‚ü©. ‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®p,q‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. ‚ü®p`n,q`n‚ü©‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ}}"
      unfolding internal_rel_def[OF assms].
    then obtain q p where q:"t=‚ü®hyper_rel``{q},hyper_rel``{p}‚ü©" "q:Pi(I,X)" "p:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®q`n,p`n‚ü©‚ààS`n}‚ààùîâ"
      by auto
    from q(1-3) have "t‚ààhyper_set√óhyper_set" unfolding hyper_set_def quotient_def by auto
  }
  then show "internal_rel(S) ‚äÜ hyper_set√óhyper_set" by auto
qed

lemma converse_internal:
  assumes "S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  shows "converse(internal_rel(S)) = internal_rel({‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})"
proof
  have "‚ãÄi. i‚ààI ‚üπ (S`i) ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" using apply_type[OF assms] by auto
  then have "‚ãÄi. i‚ààI ‚üπ converse(S`i) ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" unfolding converse_def by auto
  then have A:"{‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  {
    fix x assume "x‚ààconverse(internal_rel(S))"
    then obtain y z where x:"x=‚ü®y,z‚ü©" "‚ü®z,y‚ü©‚ààinternal_rel(S)" using converse_iff by auto
    from x(2) obtain zz yy where q:"zz:Pi(I,X)" "yy:Pi(I,X)" "z=hyper_rel``{zz}"  "y=hyper_rel``{yy}" 
      "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®zz ` n, yy ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚àà ùîâ" 
      unfolding internal_rel_def[OF assms] by auto
    from q(5) have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®yy ` n, zz ` n‚ü© ‚àà converse(S ` n)}:ùîâ" using converse_iff by auto
    then have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®yy ` n, zz ` n‚ü© ‚àà {‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}:ùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ A] by auto
    with q(1-4) x(1) have "x‚ààinternal_rel({‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" unfolding internal_rel_def[OF A] by auto
  }
  then show "converse(internal_rel(S)) ‚äÜ internal_rel({‚ü®i, converse(S ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I})" by auto
  {
    fix x assume "x‚ààinternal_rel({‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})"
    then obtain zz yy where q:"zz:Pi(I,X)" "yy:Pi(I,X)" "x=‚ü®hyper_rel``{zz},hyper_rel``{yy}‚ü©" 
      "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®zz ` n, yy ` n‚ü© ‚àà {‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI} ` n} ‚àà ùîâ" 
      unfolding internal_rel_def[OF A] by auto
    from q(4) have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®zz ` n, yy ` n‚ü© ‚àà converse(S ` n)} ‚àà ùîâ"  using apply_equality[OF _ A] by auto
    then have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®yy ` n, zz ` n‚ü© ‚àà (S ` n)} ‚àà ùîâ" using converse_iff by auto
    then have "‚ü®hyper_rel``{yy},hyper_rel``{zz}‚ü©‚ààinternal_rel(S)" unfolding internal_rel_def[OF assms]
      using q(1,2) by auto
    then have "x:converse(internal_rel(S))" using q(3) converse_iff by auto
  }
  then show "internal_rel({‚ü®i,converse(S`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}) ‚äÜ converse(internal_rel(S))" by auto
qed
    

lemma internal_rel_total:
  shows "internal_rel({‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}) = hyper_set√óhyper_set"
proof
  have f:"{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  then show "internal_rel({‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}) ‚äÜ hyper_set√óhyper_set" using internal_rel_subset by auto
  {
    fix m assume "m‚ààhyper_set√óhyper_set"
    then obtain m1 m2 where p:"m1‚ààhyper_set" "m2‚ààhyper_set" "m=‚ü®m1,m2‚ü©" by auto
    then obtain x1 x2 where m:"m1=hyper_rel``{x1}" "m2=hyper_rel``{x2}" "m=‚ü®m1,m2‚ü©"
      "x1‚ààPi(I,X)" "x2‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding hyper_set_def quotient_def by auto
    {
      fix n assume n:"n‚ààI"
      with m have "‚ü®x1`n,x2`n‚ü©‚ààX(n)√óX(n)" using apply_type by auto
      then have "‚ü®x1`n,x2`n‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n" using apply_equality[OF _ f] n by auto
    }
    then have "I={n‚ààI. ‚ü®x1`n,x2`n‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}" by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®x1`n,x2`n‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}:ùîâ" using
        ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "‚ü®x1,x2‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®p,q‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. ‚ü®p`n,q`n‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ}"
      using m(4,5) by auto
    with m(1,2) have "‚ü®m1,m2‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®hyper_rel``{x1},hyper_rel``{x2}‚ü©. ‚ü®x1,x2‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®p,q‚ü©‚ààPi(I,X)√óPi(I,X). {n‚ààI. ‚ü®p`n,q`n‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}‚ààùîâ}}"
      by auto
    with p(3) have "m‚ààinternal_rel({‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})"
      unfolding internal_rel_def[OF f] by auto
  }
  then show "hyper_set√óhyper_set ‚äÜ internal_rel({‚ü®i,X(i)√óX(i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
qed

subsection‚ÄπInternal functions‚Ä∫

definition internal_fun where
"S1:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i))) ‚üπ S2:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i))) ‚üπ S:Pi(I, Œªi. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i) 
  ‚üπ internal_fun(S) ‚â° internal_rel(S)"


lemma internal_fun_is_fun:
  assumes "S1:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "S2:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" "S:Pi(I, Œªi. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i)"
  shows "internal_fun(S):internal_set(S1)‚Üíinternal_set(S2)" "S:Pi(I, Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def
proof(safe)
  have SS:"S:Pi(I, Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  proof-
    {
      fix x assume "x‚ààS"
      with assms(3) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then obtain i f where f:"x=‚ü®i,f‚ü©" "i‚ààI" "f‚ààS1`i ‚Üí S2`i" by auto
      from f(3) have "f ‚äÜ S1`i√óS2`i" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then have "f ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(1) f(2)] apply_type[OF assms(2) f(2)] by auto
      with f(1,2) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    }
    then have "S ‚äÜ (‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    then show ?thesis using assms(3) unfolding Pi_def by auto
  qed
  from SS show "‚ãÄx. x ‚àà S ‚üπ x ‚àà (‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i) √ó X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def by auto
  from SS show "‚ãÄx. x ‚àà I ‚üπ x ‚àà domain(S)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
  from SS show "‚ãÄx y y'. ‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà S ‚üπ ‚ü®x, y'‚ü© ‚àà S ‚üπ y = y'" unfolding Pi_def function_def by blast
  fix x assume x:"x‚ààinternal_fun(S)"
  then obtain y z where f:"x= ‚ü®hyper_rel``{y},hyper_rel``{z}‚ü©" "y:Pi(I,X)" "z:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®y`n, z`n‚ü©:S`n}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding internal_fun_def[OF assms] internal_rel_def[OF SS] by auto
  {
    fix n assume n:"n:{n‚ààI. ‚ü®y`n, z`n‚ü©:S`n}"
    then have n:"n:I" "‚ü®y`n,z`n‚ü©:S`n" by auto
    moreover from n(1) have "S`n‚àà S1`n ‚Üí S2`n" using apply_type[OF assms(3)] by auto
    with n(2) have "y`n:S1`n" "z`n:S2`n" unfolding Pi_def by auto
    with n(1) have "n‚àà{n:I. y`n:S1`n}" "n‚àà{n:I. z`n:S2`n}" by auto
  }
  then have s:"{n‚ààI. ‚ü®y`n, z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. y`n:S1`n}" "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®y`n, z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. z`n:S2`n}" by auto
  from f(4) have R:"‚ãÄA. A‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ {n‚ààI. ‚ü®y`n, z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ A ‚üπ A‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def
    by auto
  from R[of "{n:I. y`n:S1`n}"] s(1) have "{n:I. y`n:S1`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
  then have "hyper_rel``{y}:internal_set(S1)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)]
    using f(2) by auto moreover
  from R[of "{n:I. z`n:S2`n}"] s(2) have "{n:I. z`n:S2`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
  then have "hyper_rel``{z}:internal_set(S2)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(2)]
    using f(3) by auto moreover note f(1)
  ultimately show "x‚ààinternal_set(S1)√óinternal_set(S2)" by auto
next
  have SS:"S:Pi(I, Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  proof-
    {
      fix x assume "x‚ààS"
      with assms(3) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then obtain i f where f:"x=‚ü®i,f‚ü©" "i‚ààI" "f‚ààS1`i ‚Üí S2`i" by auto
      from f(3) have "f ‚äÜ S1`i√óS2`i" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then have "f ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(1) f(2)] apply_type[OF assms(2) f(2)] by auto
      with f(1,2) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    }
    then have "S ‚äÜ (‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    then show ?thesis using assms(3) unfolding Pi_def by auto
  qed
  fix x assume "x‚ààinternal_set(S1)"
  then obtain y where x:"x=hyper_rel``{y}" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n}:ùîâ"
    unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
  let ?z="{‚ü®i,if y`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(y`i) else y`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  have z:"?z‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto prefer 2
    using x(2) apply_type apply simp
  proof-
    fix i assume i:"i:I" "y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i"
    from i(1) assms(3) have "S`i:S1`i ‚Üí S2`i" using apply_type by auto
    with i(2) have "(S`i)`(y`i):S2`i" using apply_type by auto
    with i(1) show "(S`i)`(y`i):X(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(2)] by auto
  qed
  {
    fix n assume "n‚àà{n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n}"
    then have n:"n:I" "y`n:S1`n" by auto
    from assms(3) n(1) have "S`n‚ààS1`n ‚Üí S2`n" using apply_type by auto
    with n(2) have "‚ü®y`n,(S`n)`(y`n)‚ü©‚ààS`n" using apply_Pair by auto
    with n(1) have "n‚àà{n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n}" using n(2) apply_equality[OF _ z] by auto
  }
  then have "{n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ {n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n}" by auto
  moreover have "‚àÄC‚ààPow(I). {n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ C ‚ü∂ C ‚àà ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter x(3) unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  then have "{n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n}:Pow(I) ‚ü∂ ({n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ {n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚ü∂ {n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚àà ùîâ)"
    unfolding Ball_def by auto
  then have "{n:I. y`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ {n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚ü∂ {n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚àà ùîâ" by auto
  ultimately have "{n:I.  ‚ü®y`n, ?z`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚àà ùîâ" by auto
  then have "‚ü®hyper_rel``{y},hyper_rel``{?z}‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)"
    using z x(2,3) unfolding internal_fun_def[OF assms] internal_rel_def[OF SS] by auto
  then show "x‚ààdomain(internal_fun(S))" using x(1) unfolding domain_def by auto
next
  have SS:"S:Pi(I, Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  proof-
    {
      fix x assume "x‚ààS"
      with assms(3) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then obtain i f where f:"x=‚ü®i,f‚ü©" "i‚ààI" "f‚ààS1`i ‚Üí S2`i" by auto
      from f(3) have "f ‚äÜ S1`i√óS2`i" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then have "f ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(1) f(2)] apply_type[OF assms(2) f(2)] by auto
      with f(1,2) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    }
    then have "S ‚äÜ (‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    then show ?thesis using assms(3) unfolding Pi_def by auto
  qed
  fix x y z assume as:"‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)" "‚ü®x,z‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)"
  from as(1) obtain h j where f:"x= hyper_rel``{h}" "y=hyper_rel``{j}" "h:Pi(I,X)" "j:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding internal_fun_def[OF assms] internal_rel_def[OF SS] by auto
  from as(2) obtain k m where g:"x=hyper_rel``{m}" "z=hyper_rel``{k}" "m:Pi(I,X)" "k:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding internal_fun_def[OF assms] internal_rel_def[OF SS] using f(1) by auto
  from f(1) g(1) have "hyper_rel``{h} = hyper_rel``{m}" by auto
  then have "‚ü®h,m‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using same_image_equiv[OF hyper_equiv] g(3) by auto
  then have "{n:I. h`n = m`n}:ùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  with f(5) have "{n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  with g(5) have "{n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  then have "‚àÄA‚ààPow(I). {n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ A ‚ü∂ A‚ààùîâ" 
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  then have "{n:I. j`n=k`n}:Pow(I) ‚üπ {n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. j`n=k`n} ‚ü∂ {n:I. j`n=k`n}‚ààùîâ"
    by auto
  then have "{n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. j`n=k`n} ‚ü∂ {n:I. j`n=k`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto moreover
  {
    fix n assume "n:{n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n}"
    then have n:"n‚ààI" "h`n=m`n" "‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n" "‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n" by auto
    with apply_type[OF assms(3) n(1)] have "j`n=k`n" unfolding Pi_def function_def by force
    with n(1) have "n:{n:I. j`n=k`n}" by auto
  }
  then have "{n:I. h`n = m`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®h`n, j`n‚ü©:S`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ‚ü®m`n, k`n‚ü©:S`n} ‚äÜ {n:I. j`n=k`n}" by auto
  ultimately have "{n:I. j`n=k`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
  with f(4) g(4) have "‚ü®j,k‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  with f(2) g(2) show "y=z" using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv] by auto
qed

lemma internal_fun_apply:
  assumes "S1 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S2 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. S1 ` i ‚Üí S2 ` i)" 
    and "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{i:I. x`i‚ààS1`i}‚ààùîâ" (*[x]‚ààinternal_set(S1)*)
  shows "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (x ` i) else x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
    and "{‚ü®i, if x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (x ` i) else x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}:Pi(I,X)"
proof- 
  have SS:"S:Pi(I, Œªi. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))"
  proof-
    {
      fix x assume "x‚ààS"
      with assms(3) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. S1`i ‚Üí S2`i)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then obtain i f where f:"x=‚ü®i,f‚ü©" "i‚ààI" "f‚ààS1`i ‚Üí S2`i" by auto
      from f(3) have "f ‚äÜ S1`i√óS2`i" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      then have "f ‚äÜ X(i)√óX(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(1) f(2)] apply_type[OF assms(2) f(2)] by auto
      with f(1,2) have "x‚àà(‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    }
    then have "S ‚äÜ (‚àëi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)√óX(i)))" by auto
    then show ?thesis using assms(3) unfolding Pi_def by auto
  qed
  let ?z="{‚ü®i, if x`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(x`i) else x`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  show z:"?z‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto prefer 2
    using assms(4) apply_type apply simp
  proof-
    fix i assume i:"i:I" "x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i"
    from i(1) assms(3) have "S`i:S1`i ‚Üí S2`i" using apply_type by auto
    with i(2) have "(S`i)`(x`i):S2`i" using apply_type by auto
    with i(1) show "(S`i)`(x`i):X(i)" using apply_type[OF assms(2)] by auto
  qed
  have "hyper_rel``{x}‚ààinternal_set(S1)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)]
    using assms(4,5) by auto
  then have "‚ü®hyper_rel``{x},internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x})‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)"
    using apply_Pair internal_fun_is_fun[OF assms(1-3)] by auto
  then have "‚ü®hyper_rel``{x},internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x})‚ü©‚àà{‚ü®hyper_rel``{x},hyper_rel``{y}‚ü©.
    ‚ü®x,y‚ü© ‚àà {‚ü®p,q‚ü© ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. X(i)) √ó (‚àèi‚ààI. X(i)) . {n ‚àà I . ‚ü®p ` n, q ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚àà ùîâ}}"
    unfolding internal_fun_def[OF assms(1-3)] internal_rel_def[OF SS] by auto
  then obtain t y where A:"hyper_rel``{x}=hyper_rel``{t}" "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x}) = hyper_rel``{y}"
    "t:Pi(I,X)" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®t ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚àà ùîâ" by auto
  from A(1,3) assms(4) have "‚ü®x,t‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using eq_equiv_class hyper_equiv by auto
  then have "{i:I. x`i = t`i}:ùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  with A(5) have "{i:I. x`i = t`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®t ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
    unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
  have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  ultimately have "{i:I. x`i = t`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®t ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚äÜ {n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚ü∂ {n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
  {
    fix i assume "i‚àà{i:I. x`i = t`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®t ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}"
    then have "i: I" "x`i=t`i" "‚ü®t ` i, y ` i‚ü© ‚àà S ` i" by auto
    then have "i:I" "‚ü®x`i,y`i‚ü©‚ààS`i" by auto
    then have "i‚àà{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}" by auto
  }
  then have "{i:I. x`i = t`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®t ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚äÜ {n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}" by auto
  ultimately have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}:ùîâ" by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  ultimately have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n}‚ààùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def
    by auto moreover
  {
    fix n assume "n:{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n}"
    then have n:"n‚ààI" "‚ü®x`n,y`n‚ü©‚ààS`n" by auto
    from n(1) have "S`n:S1`n‚ÜíS2`n" using apply_type[OF assms(3)] by auto
    with n(2) have "‚ü®x`n,y`n‚ü©‚ààS`n" "x`n‚ààS1`n" "(S`n)`(x`n) = y`n"
      using apply_equality[of "x`n" "y`n" "S`n" "S1`n" "Œª_. S2`n"] unfolding Pi_def by auto
    then have "(if x`n‚ààS1`n then (S`n)`(x`n) else x`n) = y`n" by auto
    with n(1) have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n}" using apply_equality z by auto
  }
  then have "{n ‚àà I . ‚ü®x ` n, y ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n}" by auto
  ultimately have "{n‚ààI. ?z`n = y`n}‚ààùîâ" by auto
  then have "‚ü®?z,y‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def using A(4) z by auto
  then have "‚ü®y,?z‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using hyper_sym unfolding sym_def by auto
  then have "hyper_rel``{y} = hyper_rel``{?z}" using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv]
    by auto
  with A(2) show "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (x ` i) else x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}" by auto
qed

lemma internal_fun_apply_2:
  assumes "S1 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S2 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. S1 ` i ‚Üí S2 ` i)" 
    and "hyper_rel``{x}‚ààinternal_set(S1)"
  shows "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{x}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (x ` i) else x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
    and "{‚ü®i, if x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (x ` i) else x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}:Pi(I,X)"
  apply (rule internal_fun_apply) using assms(1) apply simp using assms(2) apply simp
  using assms(3) apply simp prefer 3 apply (rule internal_fun_apply)
  using assms(1) apply simp using assms(2) apply simp
  using assms(3) apply simp 
proof-
  from assms(4) obtain y where A:"hyper_rel``{x} = hyper_rel``{y}" "y:Pi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
  from eq_equiv_class[OF A(1) hyper_equiv A(2)] show "x:Pi(I,X)" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  then show "x‚ààPi(I,X)" by auto
  from eq_equiv_class[OF A(1) hyper_equiv A(2)] have "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n}:ùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  with A(3) have "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n} ‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  moreover have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS1`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  ultimately have "{n‚ààI. x`n = y`n} ‚à©{n‚ààI. y`n‚ààS1`n} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS1`n} ‚ü∂ {n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS1`n}:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  then show "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS1`n}:ùîâ" by auto
  then show "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààS1`n}:ùîâ" by auto
qed
  
lemma internal_fun_inj:
  assumes "S1 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S2 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. S1 ` i ‚Üí S2 ` i)" 
    and "{i:I. S`i:inj(S1`i,S2`i)}‚ààùîâ"
  shows "internal_fun(S)‚ààinj(internal_set(S1), internal_set(S2))"
  unfolding inj_def
proof(safe)
  from internal_fun_is_fun[OF assms(1-3)] show "internal_fun(S) ‚àà internal_set(S1) ‚Üí internal_set(S2)" by auto
  fix w x assume as:"x‚ààinternal_set(S1)" "w‚ààinternal_set(S1)" "internal_fun(S)`w = internal_fun(S)`x"
  from as(1,2) obtain xx wx where p:"xx:Pi(I,X)" "wx‚ààPi(I,X)" "{i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚ààùîâ"  "{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚ààùîâ"
    "x=hyper_rel``{xx}" "w=hyper_rel``{wx}"
    unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
  from as have ap:"hyper_rel ``
    {{‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}} =
hyper_rel `` {{‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}" using internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3)] p(5,6)
    by auto moreover
  have ff:"{‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ààPi(I,X)"
    "{‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ààPi(I,X)"
    using apply_type[OF assms(1)] apply_type[OF apply_type[OF assms(3)]] unfolding Pi_def function_def
    apply auto prefer 2 using apply_type[OF p(2)] apply simp
    using apply_type[OF assms(2)] apply blast
     prefer 2 using apply_type[OF p(1)] apply simp
    using apply_type[OF assms(2)] by blast
  ultimately have "‚ü®{‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}, {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
    using eq_equiv_class[OF _ hyper_equiv, of "{‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}" "{‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}"]
    by auto
  then have Q:"{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i}‚ààùîâ"
    unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
  have R:"‚ãÄx y. x‚ààùîâ ‚üπ y‚ààùîâ ‚üπ x‚à©y‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  from p(3,4) have "{i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
    unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  then have "‚ãÄQ. Q:ùîâ ‚üπ {i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©Q‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
    unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  with Q have "{i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i}‚ààùîâ"
    by auto
  with assms(4) R have "({i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i})‚à©{i ‚àà I . S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)}:ùîâ"
    by auto
  then have "‚ãÄQ. Q‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ {i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i}‚à©{i ‚àà I . S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)} ‚äÜ Q ‚üπ Q:ùîâ"
    using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
  {
    fix i assume "i‚àà{i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i}‚à©{i ‚àà I . S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)}"
    then have i:"i‚ààI" "xx`i‚ààS1`i" "wx`i‚ààS1`i" "S ` i ` (xx ` i) = S ` i ` (wx ` i)" "S`i‚ààinj(S1`i,S2`i)" using apply_equality ff by auto
    from i(2-5) have "xx`i = wx`i" unfolding inj_def by auto
    with i(1) have "i‚àà{i‚ààI. xx`i = wx`i}" by auto
  }
  then have "{i‚ààI. xx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. wx`i ‚ààS1`i}‚à©{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (xx ` i) else xx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i = {‚ü®i, if wx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (wx ` i) else wx ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`i}‚à©{i ‚àà I . S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)} ‚äÜ {i‚ààI. xx`i = wx`i}" by auto
  moreover have "{i‚ààI. xx`i = wx`i}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
  ultimately have "{i‚ààI. xx`i = wx`i}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def
    by auto
  then have "‚ü®xx,wx‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" unfolding hyper_rel_def using p(1,2) by auto
  then show "w = x" using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv, THEN sym] p(5,6) by auto
qed

lemma internal_inj_fun:
  assumes "S1 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S2 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. S1 ` i ‚Üí S2 ` i)"
    and "internal_fun(S)‚ààinj(internal_set(S1), internal_set(S2))"
    and "Pi({n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)},Œªn. {‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2})‚â†0"
    and "Pi(I,X)‚â†0"
  shows "{n‚ààI. S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚ààùîâ"
proof-
  {
    assume "I-{n‚ààI. S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚ààùîâ"
    moreover have "I-{n‚ààI. S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n)} = {n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}" by auto
    ultimately have B:"{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚ààùîâ" by auto
    from assms(5) obtain q where q:"q‚ààPi({n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)},Œªn. {‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2})"
      by auto
    from assms(6) obtain x where x:"x‚ààPi(I,X)" by auto
    let ?x="{‚ü®n,if S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n) then fst(q`n) else x`n‚ü©. n‚ààI}"
    let ?y="{‚ü®n,if S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n) then snd(q`n) else x`n‚ü©. n‚ààI}"
    have fun:"?x‚ààPi(I,X)" "?y‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto
      prefer 2 using apply_type[OF x] apply simp
        prefer 3 using apply_type[OF x] apply simp
    proof-
      fix n assume ni:"n‚ààI" "S ` n ‚àâ inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)"
      then have "q`n‚àà{‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2}"
        using apply_type[OF q] by auto
      then have A:"fst(q`n)‚ààS1`n" "snd(q`n)‚ààS1`n" by auto
      from A(1) show "fst(q`n)‚ààX(n)" using apply_type[OF assms(1)] ni(1) by auto
      from A(2) show "snd(q`n)‚ààX(n)" using apply_type[OF assms(1)] ni(1) by auto
    qed
    {
      fix n assume n1:"n‚àà{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}"
      then have n:"n‚ààI" "S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)" by auto
      have "q`n‚àà{‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2}"
        using apply_type[OF q n1] by auto
      then obtain qx qy where qq:"q`n = ‚ü®qx,qy‚ü©" "qx:S1`n" "qy:S1`n" "(S`n)`qx = (S`n)`qy" "qx‚â†qy" by auto
      from fun have "?x`n=qx" "?y`n=qy" using n(2) qq(1) apply_equality[of _ _ ?x] apply_equality[of _ _ ?y]
        n(1) by auto
      with qq(1-3) have "?x`n:S1`n" "?y`n:S1`n" by auto
      with n(1) have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}" "n‚àà{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}" by auto
    }
    then have "{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}" "{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}" by auto
    moreover note B moreover have "{n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}:Pow(I)"  "{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}:Pow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have C:"{n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}‚ààùîâ" "{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}‚ààùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have el:"hyper_rel``{?x}‚ààinternal_set(S1)" "hyper_rel``{?y}‚ààinternal_set(S1)"
      using fun unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
    then have els:"internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{?x}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
      "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{?y}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
      using internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3)] by auto
    moreover from C have "{n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    with B have D:"{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚à©({n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n})‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    from el have fun_els:"{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ààPi(I,X)" 
       "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ààPi(I,X)" 
       using internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3)] by auto
    {
      fix n assume n1:"n‚àà{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}"
      then have n:"n:I" "?x`n:S1`n" "?y`n:S1`n" "S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)" by auto
      then have R:"{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n = S ` n ` (?x ` n)"
        "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n = S ` n ` (?y ` n)"
        using apply_equality fun_els by auto
      have "q`n‚àà{‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2}"
        using apply_type[OF q] n(1,4) by auto
      then obtain qx qy where qq:"q`n = ‚ü®qx,qy‚ü©" "qx:S1`n" "qy:S1`n" "(S`n)`qx = (S`n)`qy" "qx‚â†qy" by auto
      from fun have "?x`n=qx" "?y`n=qy" using n(2,3) qq(1) apply_equality[of _ _ ?x] apply_equality[of _ _ ?y]
        n(1,4) by auto
      with R n(2,3) qq(4,5) have "{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n =
        {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n" by auto
      with n(1) have "n:{n‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n =
        {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n}" by auto
    }
    then have "{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚à©({n‚ààI. ?x`n:S1`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}) ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n =
        {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n}" by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n =
        {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n}‚ààPow(I)" by auto
    moreover note D ultimately have "{n‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n =
        {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n}‚ààùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "‚ü®{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I},{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
      using fun_els unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?x ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?x ` i) else ?x ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}} =
      hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
      using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv] by auto
    with els have "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{?x}) = internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{?y})"
      by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{?x} = hyper_rel``{?y}" using assms(4)
      unfolding inj_def[of "internal_set(S1)" "internal_set(S2)"] using el
      by auto
    then have "‚ü®?x,?y‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel" using eq_equiv_class[OF _ hyper_equiv] fun by auto
    then have "{n‚ààI. ?x`n = ?y`n}‚ààùîâ" unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    with B have "{n‚ààI. ?x`n = ?y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}‚ààùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    {
      fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. ?x`n = ?y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)}"
       then have n:"n‚ààI" "S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)" "?x`n =?y`n" by auto
      have "q`n‚àà{‚ü®q1,q2‚ü©‚ààS1`n√óS1`n. (S`n)`q1 = (S`n)`q2 ‚àß q1‚â†q2}"
        using apply_type[OF q] n by auto
      then obtain qx qy where qq:"q`n = ‚ü®qx,qy‚ü©" "qx:S1`n" "qy:S1`n" "(S`n)`qx = (S`n)`qy" "qx‚â†qy" by auto
      from fun have "?x`n=qx" "?y`n=qy" using n(2) qq(1) apply_equality[of _ _ ?x] apply_equality[of _ _ ?y]
        n(1) by auto
      with qq(5) n(3) have False by auto
    }
    then have "{n‚ààI. ?x`n = ?y`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)} = 0" by auto
    ultimately have "0:ùîâ" by auto
    then have False using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
  }
  then show "{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)} ‚àà ùîâ"
    using set_ultrafilter[OF _ ultraFilter] by auto
qed


lemma internal_fun_converse:
  assumes "S1 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S2 ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" "S ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. S1 ` i ‚Üí S2 ` i)"
    and "internal_fun(S)‚ààbij(internal_set(S1), B)" and "(‚àèn‚àà{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àâ inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)}.
      {‚ü®q1,q2‚ü© ‚àà S1 ` n √ó S1 ` n . S ` n ` q1 = S ` n ` q2 ‚àß q1 ‚â† q2}) ‚â† 0"
  defines "SS ‚â° {‚ü®i, if S`i‚ààinj(S1`i,S2`i) then converse(S`i) else 0‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  shows "converse(internal_fun(S)) = internal_fun(SS)"
  apply(rule fun_extension[of "converse(internal_fun(S))" B "Œª_. internal_set(S1)" 
      "internal_fun(SS)" "Œª_. internal_set(S1)"])
proof-
  let ?S1'= "{‚ü®i,if S`i‚ààinj(S1`i,S2`i) then S1`i else 0‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  let ?S2'= "{‚ü®i,if S`i‚ààinj(S1`i,S2`i) then S2`i else 0‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  let ?S' = "{‚ü®i, if S`i‚ààinj(S1`i,S2`i) then S`i else 0‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  from assms(4) have "converse(internal_fun(S))‚ààbij(B,internal_set(S1))"
    using bij_converse_bij by auto
  then show CC:"converse(internal_fun(S)):B ‚Üí internal_set(S1)" using bij_is_fun by auto
  from internal_fun_is_fun[OF assms(1-3)] have F:"internal_fun(S):internal_set(S1)‚Üíinternal_set(S2)"
    by auto
  then have INJ:"internal_fun(S)‚ààinj(internal_set(S1),internal_set(S2))"
    using bij_is_inj[OF assms(4)] unfolding inj_def by auto
  have S1:"?S1'‚àà(‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto
    using if_iff apply auto using apply_type[OF assms(1)] by auto
  have S2:"?S2'‚àà(‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto
    using if_iff apply auto using apply_type[OF assms(2)] by auto
  have S:"?S'‚àà(‚àèi‚ààI. ?S1'`i ‚Üí ?S2'`i)" unfolding Pi_def
    function_def apply auto
  proof-
    {
      fix i x assume as:"i‚ààI" "x ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then S ` i else 0)"
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(2) have "x‚ààS`i" by auto moreover
        from A have "?S1'`i =S1`i" using apply_equality[OF _ S1] as(1) by auto
        moreover from A have "?S2'`i =S2`i" using apply_equality[OF _ S2] as(1) by auto
        moreover from as(1) have "S`i:S1`i‚ÜíS2`i" using apply_type[OF assms(3)] by auto
        ultimately have "x‚àà?S1'`i√ó?S2'`i" unfolding Pi_def by auto
      } moreover
      {
        assume A:"S`i‚àâinj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(2) have False by auto
      }
      ultimately show "x‚àà?S1'`i√ó?S2'`i" by auto
    }
    {
      fix i x assume as:"i ‚àà I" "x ‚àà ?S1' ` i" "S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
      from as(3) have "?S1'`i =S1`i" using apply_equality[OF _ S1] as(1) by auto
      with as(2) show "x‚ààdomain(S`i)" using apply_type[OF assms(3)] as(1) unfolding Pi_def by auto
    }
    {
      fix i x assume as:"i ‚àà I" "x ‚àà ?S1' ` i" 
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àâ inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        from A have "?S1'`i = 0" using apply_equality[OF _ S1] as(1) by auto
        with as have False by auto
      }
      then show "S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)" by auto
    }
    {
      fix i x y y' assume as:"i ‚àà I"
       "‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then S ` i else 0)"
       "‚ü®x, y'‚ü© ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then S ` i else 0)"
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àâ inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(2) have False by auto
      }
      then have inj:"S`i‚ààinj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)" by auto
      then have "S`i:S1`i ‚Üí S2`i" unfolding inj_def by auto moreover
      from inj as(2,3) have "‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚ààS`i" "‚ü®x,y'‚ü©‚ààS`i" by auto
      ultimately show "y=y'" unfolding Pi_def function_def by blast
    }
  qed
  let ?S2="{‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}"
  {
    fix i assume i:"i‚ààI"
    then have "?S'`i:?S1'`i ‚Üí ?S2'`i" using apply_type[OF S] by auto
    then have "range(?S'`i) ‚äÜ ?S2'`i" using func1_1_L5B by auto
    then have "range(?S'`i) ‚äÜ X(i)" using apply_type[OF S2 i] by auto
  }
  then have SS2:"?S2‚àà(‚àèi‚ààI. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def function_def by auto
  have SS:"SS‚àà(‚àèi‚ààI. range(?S'`i) ‚Üí S1`i)" unfolding SS_def Pi_def
    function_def apply auto
  proof-
    {
      fix i x assume as:"i ‚àà I"
       "x ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then converse(S ` i) else 0)"
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(2) have "x:converse(S`i)" by auto
        then obtain x1 x2 where x:"‚ü®x2,x1‚ü©‚ààS`i" "x=‚ü®x1,x2‚ü©" unfolding converse_def by auto
        from as(1) have "S`i:S1`i‚ÜíS2`i" using apply_type[OF assms(3)] by auto
        then have "S`i:S1`i‚Üírange(S`i)" using range_of_fun by auto
        with x(1) have "x2‚ààS1`i" "x1‚ààrange(S`i)" unfolding Pi_def by auto
        with x(2) have "x‚ààrange(S`i)√óS1`i" by auto
        moreover have "?S'`i = S`i" using apply_equality[OF _ S, of i] as(1) A
          by auto
        ultimately have "x ‚àà range(?S' ` i) √ó S1 ` i" by auto
      }moreover
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àâ inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(2) have False by auto
      } ultimately
      show "x‚ààrange(?S'`i)√óS1`i" by auto
    }
    {
      fix i x y assume as:"i ‚àà I" "‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà ?S' ` i" "S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
      from as(1,3) have "?S' `i = S`i" using apply_equality[OF _ S, of i] as(1)
        by auto
      with as(2) have "‚ü®x,y‚ü©‚ààS`i" by auto
      then show "y‚ààrange(S`i)" using rangeI by auto
    }
    {
      fix i x y assume as:"i ‚àà I" "‚ü®x, y‚ü© ‚àà ?S' ` i"
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àâ inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(1,2) have False using apply_equality[OF _ S] by auto
      }
      then show "S`i:inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)" by auto
    }
    {
      fix i xa y y' assume as:"i ‚àà I"
       "‚ü®xa, y‚ü© ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then converse(S ` i) else 0)"
       "‚ü®xa, y'‚ü© ‚àà (if S ` i ‚àà inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i) then converse(S ` i) else 0)"
      {
        assume A:"S ` i ‚àâ inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)"
        with as(1,2) have False using apply_equality[OF _ S] by auto
      }
      then have A:"S`i:inj(S1 ` i, S2 ` i)" by auto
      with as(2,3) have "‚ü®xa,y‚ü©‚ààconverse(S`i)" "‚ü®xa,y'‚ü©‚ààconverse(S`i)" by auto
      then have "‚ü®y,xa‚ü©:S`i" "‚ü®y',xa‚ü©:S`i" unfolding converse_def by auto
      moreover then have "y‚ààS1`i" "y'‚ààS1`i" "(S`i)`y=xa" "(S`i)`y'=xa" using apply_type[OF assms(3) as(1)]
        unfolding Pi_def using apply_equality[OF _ inj_is_fun[OF A]] by auto moreover note A
      ultimately show "y=y'" unfolding inj_def by auto
    }
  qed
  then have T:"SS ‚àà (‚àèi‚ààI. {‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I} ` i ‚Üí S1 ` i)"
    using apply_equality[OF _ SS2] unfolding Pi_def Sigma_def by auto
  from internal_fun_is_fun(1)[OF SS2 assms(1) this]
  have Q:"internal_fun(SS) ‚àà
  internal_set({‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I}) ‚Üí internal_set(S1)" by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààinternal_set({‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I})"
    then obtain x where x:"t=hyper_rel``{x}" "x‚ààPi(I,X)" "{n‚ààI. x`n‚àà{‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`n}:ùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF SS2] by auto
    from x(3) have P:"{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààrange(?S' ` n)}:ùîâ" using apply_equality[OF _ SS2]
      by auto
    let ?y="{‚ü®n,if S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n) ‚àß x`n‚ààrange(S`n) then (converse(S`n)`(x`n)) else x`n‚ü©. n‚ààI}"
    have Y:"?y‚ààPi(I,X)" unfolding Pi_def function_def apply auto
      prefer 2 using apply_type[OF x(2)] apply simp
      prefer 2 using apply_type[OF x(2)] apply simp
    proof-
      fix n xa assume n:"n:I" "S`n:inj(S1`n,S2`n)" "‚ü®xa, x ` n‚ü© ‚àà S ` n"
      from n(2) have "converse(S`n):range(S`n) ‚Üí S1`n" using inj_converse_fun by auto
      then have "converse(S`n)`(x`n) = xa" using apply_equality n(3) converse_iff[of "x`n" xa]
        by auto
      moreover from n(2,3) have "xa‚ààS1`n" unfolding inj_def Pi_def by auto
      then have "xa‚ààX(n)" using apply_type[OF assms(1)] n(1) by auto
      ultimately show "converse(S`n)`(x`n)‚ààX(n)" by auto
    qed
    {
      fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààrange(?S' ` n)}"
      then have n:"n:I" "x`n:range(?S'`n)" by auto
      from n(1) have "?S'`n:?S1'`n‚Üí?S2'`n" using apply_type S by auto
      {
        assume "S`n‚àâinj(S1`n,S2`n)"
        then have "?S'`n = 0" using apply_equality[OF _ S] n(1) by auto
        then have "range(?S'`n) = 0" by auto
        with n(2) have False by auto
      }
      then have Z:"S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n)" by auto
      then have "?S'`n = S`n" using n(1) apply_equality[OF _ S] by auto
      with n(2) have n2:"x`n:range(S`n)" by auto
      have "?y`n = (if (S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n) ‚àß x ` n ‚àà range(S ` n)) then converse(S ` n) ` (x ` n)
         else (x ` n))" using apply_equality[of n, OF _ Y] n(1,2) by auto moreover
      from n2 Z have "S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n) ‚àß x ` n ‚àà range(S ` n)" by blast ultimately
      have "?y`n = converse(S ` n) ` (x ` n)" by auto
      moreover from Z have "converse(S`n):range(S`n) ‚Üí S1`n" using inj_converse_fun by auto
      with n2 have "converse(S ` n) ` (x ` n):S1`n" using apply_type by auto
      ultimately have "?y`n:S1`n" by auto
      with n(1) have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}" by auto
    }
    then have Q:"{n ‚àà I . x ` n ‚àà range(?S' ` n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}" by auto
    from P have "‚ãÄQ. Q‚ààPow(I) ‚üπ {n ‚àà I . x ` n ‚àà range(?S' ` n)} ‚äÜ Q ‚üπ Q:ùîâ" using ultraFilter 
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    have "{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}:Pow(I)" by auto moreover note Q
    ultimately have B:"{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}:ùîâ" by auto
    with Y have M:"hyper_rel``{?y}‚ààinternal_set(S1)" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)]
      by auto
    with internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3)] have A:"internal_fun(S) ` ((hyper_rel) `` {?y}) =
    hyper_rel ``
    {{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}}"
      "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}:Pi(I,X)" by auto
    {
      fix t assume "t‚àà{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààrange(?S' ` n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}"
      then have t:"t‚ààI" "x`t:range(?S'`t)" "?y`t:S1`t" by auto
      from A(2) t(1,3) have "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t =
          (S ` t) ` (?y ` t)" using apply_equality by auto
      {
        assume "S`t‚àâinj(S1`t,S2`t)"
        then have "?S'`t = 0" using apply_equality[OF _ S] t(1) by auto
        then have "range(?S'`t) = 0" by auto
        with t(2) have False by auto
      }
      then have Z:"S`t:inj(S1`t,S2`t)" by auto
      then have ZZ:"?S'`t = S`t" using apply_equality[OF _ S] t(1) by auto
      with Z t(1,2) have "?y`t = converse(S ` t) ` (x ` t)" using apply_equality[OF _ Y] by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = (S`t)`(converse(S ` t) ` (x ` t))"
        using apply_equality[OF _ A(2)] t(1,3) by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = x`t"
        using right_inverse[OF Z] t(2) ZZ by auto
      with t(1) have "t‚àà{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = x`t}" by auto
    }
    then have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààrange(?S' ` n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n} ‚äÜ {t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = x`t}" by auto
    moreover have "{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = x`t}:Pow(I)" by auto
    moreover from B P have "{n‚ààI. x`n‚ààrange(?S' ` n)}‚à©{n‚ààI. ?y`n:S1`n}:ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    ultimately have "{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}`t = x`t}:ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    with A(2) x(2) have "‚ü®{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I},x‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
      unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}} = hyper_rel``{x}"
      using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv] by auto
    with x(1) have "hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if ?y ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (?y ` i) else ?y ` i‚ü© . i ‚àà I}} = t" by auto
    with A(1) have "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel ``{?y}) = t" by auto
    then have "t‚ààrange(internal_fun(S))" using apply_Pair[OF F M] rangeI by auto
    then have "t‚ààB" using surj_range[OF bij_is_surj[OF assms(4)]] by auto
  }
  then have A:"internal_set({‚ü®i, range(?S' ` i)‚ü© . i ‚àà I}) ‚äÜ B" by auto
  {
    fix t assume "t‚ààB"
    then have "t‚ààrange(internal_fun(S))" using surj_range[OF bij_is_surj[OF assms(4)]] by auto
    then obtain q where q:"‚ü®q,t‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)" using rangeE by auto
    then have q2:"internal_fun(S)`q = t" using apply_equality[OF _ bij_is_fun[OF assms(4)]] by auto
    from q have s:"q‚ààinternal_set(S1)" "t‚ààinternal_set(S2)" using bij_is_fun[OF assms(4)] F unfolding Pi_def by auto
    then obtain qx where x:"qx‚ààPi(I,X)" "hyper_rel``{qx} = q" "{n‚ààI. qx`n‚ààS1`n}:ùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
    from s x(2) have f:"internal_fun(S)`q = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i,if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i‚ü©. i‚ààI}}"
      "{‚ü®i,if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,X)"
      using internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3), of qx] by auto
    from f(1) q2 have "hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i,if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i‚ü©. i‚ààI}} = t" by auto
    moreover from s(2) obtain tx where xx:"tx:Pi(I,X)" "hyper_rel``{tx} = t" "{n‚ààI. tx`n‚ààS2`n}:ùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(2)] by auto
    note xx(2) ultimately have "‚ü®{‚ü®i,if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i‚ü©. i‚ààI},tx‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
      using eq_equiv_class[OF _ hyper_equiv xx(1)] by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. {‚ü®i,if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i=tx`i}‚ààùîâ"
      unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "{i‚ààI. (if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i)=tx`i}‚ààùîâ"
      using f(2) apply_equality by auto
    with x(3) have "{n‚ààI. qx`n‚ààS1`n}‚à©{i‚ààI. (if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i)=tx`i}‚ààùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    from internal_inj_fun[OF assms(1-3) INJ assms(5)] xx(1) have 
      "{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)} ‚àà ùîâ" by auto ultimately
    have "({n‚ààI. qx`n‚ààS1`n}‚à©{i‚ààI. (if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i)=tx`i})‚à©{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)} ‚àà ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    {
      fix n assume "n‚àà{n‚ààI. qx`n‚ààS1`n}‚à©{i‚ààI. (if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i)=tx`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)}"
      then have n1:"n‚ààI" "qx`n:S1`n" "(if qx ` n ‚àà S1 ` n then S ` n ` (qx ` n) else qx ` n)=tx`n" "S`n‚ààinj(S1`n,S2`n)" by auto
      from n1(2,3) have "S ` n ` (qx ` n) = tx`n" by auto
      then have "tx`n ‚àà range(S`n)" using rangeI[OF apply_Pair[OF apply_type[OF assms(3) n1(1)] n1(2)]] by auto
      then have "tx`n‚ààrange(?S'`n)" using apply_equality[of n "S`n", OF _ S] using n1(1,4) by auto
      with n1(1) have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. tx`n‚ààrange(?S'`n)}" by auto
      moreover have "{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n = range(?S'`n)" using apply_equality[of n "range(?S'`n)" 
            "{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}" I "Œª_. {range(?S'`i). i‚ààI}"] n1(1) unfolding Pi_def function_def
        by auto
      ultimately have "n‚àà{n‚ààI. tx`n‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}" by auto
    }
    then have "{n‚ààI. qx`n‚ààS1`n}‚à©{i‚ààI. (if qx ` i ‚àà S1 ` i then S ` i ` (qx ` i) else qx ` i)=tx`i}‚à©{n ‚àà I . S ` n ‚àà inj(S1 ` n, S2 ` n)} ‚äÜ {n‚ààI. tx`n‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}" by auto
    moreover have "{n‚ààI. tx`n‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}:Pow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have "{n‚ààI. tx`n‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{tx}‚ààinternal_set({‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF SS2] using xx(1) by auto
    with xx(2) have "t‚ààinternal_set({‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
  }
  then have "B ‚äÜ internal_set({‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
  with A have eq:"B = internal_set({‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
  from subst[OF this[THEN sym], of "ŒªB. internal_fun(SS) ‚àà B ‚Üí internal_set(S1)"] Q 
  show "internal_fun(SS) ‚àà B ‚Üí internal_set(S1)" by auto
  {
    fix x assume as:"x‚ààB"
    with eq have xx:"x‚ààinternal_set({‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI})" by auto
    then obtain xx where x:"xx‚ààPi(I,X)" "x=hyper_rel``{xx}" "{i‚ààI. xx`i‚ààrange(?S'`i)}:ùîâ"
      unfolding internal_set_def[OF SS2] using apply_equality[OF _ SS2] by auto
    have M:"internal_fun(SS)`x = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}}"
      "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}:Pi(I,X)"
      using internal_fun_apply_2[OF SS2 assms(1) T, of xx] xx x(2) by auto
    have "internal_fun(S)`(converse(internal_fun(S))`x) = x"
      using right_inverse_lemma[OF F CC as] by auto 
    from as CC have A:"converse(internal_fun(S))`x :internal_set(S1)" using apply_type by auto
    then obtain yx where yx:"yx:Pi(I,X)" "converse(internal_fun(S))`x = hyper_rel``{yx}"
      "{i‚ààI. yx`i :S1`i}:ùîâ" unfolding internal_set_def[OF assms(1)] by auto
    from CC yx(2) have "‚ü®x, hyper_rel``{yx}‚ü©‚ààconverse(internal_fun(S))" 
      using apply_Pair[OF _ as, of "converse(internal_fun(S))" "Œª_. internal_set(S1)"] by auto
    then have "‚ü®hyper_rel``{yx},x‚ü©‚ààinternal_fun(S)" using converse_iff by auto
    then have "internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{yx}) = x" using apply_equality[OF _ F] by auto moreover
    have L:"internal_fun(S)`(hyper_rel``{yx}) = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if yx`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(yx`i) else yx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}}"
      "{‚ü®i, if yx`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(yx`i) else yx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}‚ààPi(I,X)"
      using internal_fun_apply_2[OF assms(1-3), of yx] A yx(2) by auto
    ultimately have "x = hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if yx`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(yx`i) else yx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}}" by auto
    with x(1,2) have "‚ü®{‚ü®i, if yx`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(yx`i) else yx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI},xx‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
      using eq_equiv_class[OF _ hyper_equiv, of _ xx] by auto
    then have "{n:I. {‚ü®i, if yx`i‚ààS1`i then (S`i)`(yx`i) else yx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`n=xx`n}:ùîâ"
      unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "{n:I. (if yx`n‚ààS1`n then (S`n)`(yx`n) else yx`n)=xx`n}:ùîâ"
      using apply_equality[OF _ L(2)] by auto
    with yx(3) have "{n:I. (if yx`n‚ààS1`n then (S`n)`(yx`n) else yx`n)=xx`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. yx`n :S1`n}:ùîâ"
      using ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    {
      fix s assume "s‚àà{n:I. (if yx`n‚ààS1`n then (S`n)`(yx`n) else yx`n)=xx`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. yx`n :S1`n}"
      then have s:"s‚ààI" "(if yx`s‚ààS1`s then (S`s)`(yx`s) else yx`s)=xx`s" "yx`s:S1`s" by auto
      then have "s‚ààI" "(S`s)`(yx`s)=xx`s" by auto
      then have "s‚ààI" "(SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s)" by auto
      with s(3) have "s‚àà{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}" by auto
    }
    then have "{n:I. (if yx`n‚ààS1`n then (S`n)`(yx`n) else yx`n)=xx`n}‚à©{n‚ààI. yx`n :S1`n} ‚äÜ {s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}" by auto
    moreover have "{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}:Pow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have "{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}‚à©{i‚ààI. xx`i‚ààrange(?S'`i)}:ùîâ"
      using x(3) ultraFilter unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto moreover
    {
      fix t assume "t‚àà{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}‚à©{i‚ààI. xx`i‚ààrange(?S'`i)}"
      then have t:"t:I" "(SS`t)`((S`t)`(yx`t)) = (SS`t)`(xx`t)" "xx`t‚ààrange(?S'`t)" "yx`t:S1`t" by auto
      {
        assume "S`t‚àâinj(S1`t,S2`t)"
        then have "?S'`t = 0" using t(1) apply_equality[OF _ S] by auto
        then have "range(?S'`t) = 0" by auto
        with t(3) have False by auto
      }
      then have INJ:"S`t:inj(S1`t,S2`t)" by auto
      from M(2) have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = (if xx`t‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t then (SS`t)`(xx`t) else xx`t)"
        using apply_equality t(1) by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = (if xx`t‚ààrange(?S'`t) then (SS`t)`(xx`t) else xx`t)"
        using apply_equality[OF _ SS2] t(1) by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = (SS`t)`(xx`t)"
        using t(3) by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = (SS`t)`((S`t)`(yx`t))"
        using t(2) by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = converse(S`t)`((S`t)`(yx`t))"
        using apply_equality[OF _ SS] t(1) INJ unfolding SS_def by auto
      then have "{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = yx`t" using left_inverse[OF INJ] t(4) by auto
      with t(1) have "t‚àà{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = yx`t}" by auto
    }
    then have "{s‚ààI. (SS`s)`((S`s)`(yx`s)) = (SS`s)`(xx`s) ‚àß yx`s‚ààS1`s}‚à©{i‚ààI. xx`i‚ààrange(?S'`i)} ‚äÜ {t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = yx`t}" by auto
    moreover have "{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = yx`t}:Pow(I)" by auto
    ultimately have "{t‚ààI. {‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}`t = yx`t}:ùîâ" using ultraFilter
      unfolding IsFilter_def IsUltrafilter_def by auto
    then have "‚ü®{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI},yx‚ü©‚ààhyper_rel"
      using M(2) yx(1) unfolding hyper_rel_def by auto
    then have "hyper_rel``{{‚ü®i, if xx`i‚àà{‚ü®i,range(?S'`i)‚ü©. i‚ààI}`i then (SS`i)`(xx`i) else xx`i‚ü©. i‚ààI}} = hyper_rel``{yx}"
      using equiv_class_eq[OF hyper_equiv] by auto
    with M(1) have "internal_fun(SS)`x = hyper_rel``{yx}" by auto
    with yx(2) have "internal_fun(SS)`x = converse(internal_fun(S))`x" by auto
    then show "converse(internal_fun(S)) ` x = internal_fun(SS) ` x" by auto
  }
qed

definition isHyperFinite where
"H‚ààPow(hyper_set) ‚üπ isHyperFinite(H) ‚â° ‚àÉS‚ààPi(I,Œªi. FinPow(X(i))). H = internal_set(S)"

lemma hyperfinite_internal:
  assumes "H‚ààPow(hyper_set)" "isHyperFinite(H)"
  shows "isInternal(H)"
proof-
  from assms(2) obtain S where S:"S:Pi(I,Œªi. FinPow(X(i)))" "H=internal_set(S)"
    unfolding isHyperFinite_def[OF assms(1)] isInternal_def by auto
  from S(1) have "S:Pi(I,Œªi. Pow(X(i)))" unfolding Pi_def FinPow_def by auto
  with S(2) show ?thesis unfolding isInternal_def by auto
qed
